, whether or not the word ‘balance sheet’ is contained in the data. Once identified, these concept attributes are stored in a relational database where they can be queried for search and understanding, trend analysis, data mining or enrichment with other structured data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"MainText\"><span class=\"header\">Taxonomy Details</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MainText\"><span class=\"SubHead\">Intellisophic taxonomies can be used by themselves or in combination with company specific taxonomies.</span> Intellisophic’s team of experts will evaluate the customer and pick the right combination of taxonomies to meet the business needs. Taxonomy details can be found by following the sector of interest below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"MainText\"><a href=\"http://localhost/intellisophic/corporate-taxonomies/\"><strong>Corporate</strong></a></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"MainText\"><a href=\"http://localhost/intellisophic/government-taxonomies/\"><strong>Government</strong></a></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"MainText\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Educational</strong></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Taxonomic Content','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2016-07-29 21:15:16','2016-07-29 21:15:16','',13,'http://localhost/intellisophic/2016/07/29/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(67,1,'2016-07-29 21:16:16','2016-07-29 21:16:16','<p class=\"MainText\">The educational taxonomies are general interest taxonomies covering history, culture, lifestyle, travel, religion and a number of other topics. Below are taxonomies of educational interest.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"SubHead\">Arts &amp; Humanities</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MainText\">Actors &amp; Managers of the English Stage; Contemporary Music; Art History; Artifacts; Architectural History; American Music; American Musical Heritage: Native American, African American, British Isles, European, Spanish American, and Asian American; Modern Art; Anthropical Literature; Armenia Art; Art Reference; Classical Mu